1) Classification Kya Hota Hai?
Classification ka matlab data ko categories (labels) me divide karna.
Example: Spam/Not Spam, Pass/Fail, Disease/No Disease.

2) Logistic Regression Kya Hai?
Ye ek classification algorithm hai jo probability (0 se 1 ke beech) nikalta hai.
Sigmoid Function use hota hai:
1 / (1 + e^-x)
Rule: Probability > 0.5 = Class 1, < 0.5 = Class 0

3) Accuracy Kya Hai?
Accuracy = Correct Predictions / Total Predictions
Ye batata hai kitni predictions sahi thi.
Note: Imbalanced data me accuracy misleading ho sakti hai.

4) Confusion Matrix
Actual vs Predicted ka table hota hai:
TP - True Positive (Sahi Positive)
TN - True Negative (Sahi Negative)
FP - False Positive (Galat Positive)
FN - False Negative (Galat Negative)

5) Important Metrics
Precision = TP / (TP + FP)
Recall = TP / (TP + FN)

F1 Score = Precision & Recall ka balance
6) Logistic Regression Flow
1. Data Cleaning
2. Train-Test Split
3. Model Create
4. Fit Model
5. Predict
6. Evaluate (Accuracy + Confusion Matrix)
Quick Revision Trick:
Linear -> Sigmoid -> Probability -> Class
